rom\": 271, \"to\": 282}, {\"ngram\": \"a campaign\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"altogetherde-Christianizethe country\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some revolutionaries went so far as to attempt to replace the longstanding statereligionwith the atheistic Cult of Reason.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some revolutionaries\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the longstanding\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"the atheistic Cult\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"Reason\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To this end, cultists swapped out the remaining religious statues in Notre Dame Cathedral for secular busts, engaged in rituals mocking those once practiced on the altar, and paraded around hyper-sexualized women, including an actress meant to portray the goddess of reason.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this end\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"cultists\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the remaining religious statues\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre Dame Cathedral\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"secular busts\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"rituals\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"the altar\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"hyper-sexualized women\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"an actress\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the goddess\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"reason\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a similar spirit, the French kicked off the 2024 Olympics with anti-Christian mockery and substitution - although this time, they opted for men pretending to be hyper-sexualized women.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\